Produce n-tuples
================

# For a local test:
heppy Multi run_susyMultilepton_cfg.py -N 1000 -o test=1 -o analysis=SOS

# For the full production (on cmsco01):
heppy_batch.py -r /store/user/bschneid/pMSSM -o run01 run_susyMultilepton_cfg.py --option analysis=SOS --option runSMS=True -b 'bsub -q 1nd -u bschneid -o std_output.txt -J mc_prod_sos  < batchScript.sh'

# To merge output
- copy the production directory (SOS_nopresel_010616) to a local fast disk (which can be /data1/botta/ but I don’t think you can write there)
-  go in it and run « downloadTreesFromEOS.py -t treeProducerSusyMultilepton . »
-  run « haddChunks.py -c --max-size=7 . »
